    • Method Detail

      • submitATMCashAmount

        void submitATMCashAmount(CashTransaction cashTransaction)
        Submits ATM cash transaction information
        Parameters:
        cashTransaction - A CashTransaction object having paydiantTransactionId, accountURI, cashAmount, cashAccessType values populated.
        Throws:
        PaydiantException - PaydiantException or an instance of a child PaydiantException class with the error status codes. See IATMCashManagerService.submitATMCashAmount(CashTransaction) for applicable error codes.
        See Also:
        IATMCashManagerFacade.submitATMCashAmount(CashTransaction), IATMCashManagerService.submitATMCashAmount(CashTransaction)

      • setATMCashServiceListener

        void setATMCashServiceListener(IATMCashServiceListener cashServiceListener)
        Sets the listener to handle ATM cash service callbacks.
        Parameters:
        cashServiceListener - The ATM cash service listener. This can be either an implementation of IATMCashServiceListener or an extended instance of ATMCashServiceListenerAdapter.
        See Also:
        IATMCashServiceListener, ATMCashServiceListenerAdapter

      • removeListener

        void removeListener()
        Removes the cash service listener and sets it to null.
